{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The only serious damage was one of the girls that came with us that night because of the explosions of the bombs died of a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a tough time, especially after we established the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we besieged by the Egyptian army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were totally cut off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only way we could go is with small planes that we would drive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was wounded slightly, no big deal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they sent me to a-- with another friend of mine from the kibbutz-- they sent us to a-- another big kibbutz where they had a Recovery Center.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we spent three weeks there getting ourselves fattened up and eat well and-- and get better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a great furlough at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How old were you at that time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My goodness, I was 18, 17. 1949, '48. 18.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] In Bulgaria, they-- they had some very tough times there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was able, because of his background, to get a job working in a warehouse as a-- in charge of the warehouse and dealing primarily in merchandise.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they were not persecuted per se, but the Jewish life was totally eliminated under the communists and that's why they were there, under the communists.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No Jewish life whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of them became more pious than the pope and some of the Jewish communists became real involved in the government and they stayed there and they wanted to show how great they were.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they really went overboard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I always said that Jewishness-- Judaism and communism just don't mix.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was offended when the communists would say they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, they were not Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't practice any Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were Jews by birth, they didn't acknowledge anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
